{"serial": "92001", "department_serial": 21, "code": "SH5005", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Introduction to Quantum Technology", "ch": "量子科技概論"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Tsai, Pin-Ju", "Jiang, Jehn-Ruey", "Cheng, Wang-Yau"], "ch": ["蔡秉儒", "江振瑞", "鄭王曜"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 5, "session": ["5", "6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "IL", "room": "113"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "理學院", "en": "College of Science"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 18, "selected": 28, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "※此課程為理學院「量子技術」學分學程之新訂必修課程。//教師預期學生在修習本課程後之學習學程，或學生應有的專業表現。強調學生修習此門課程後可展現的具體能力。本課程旨在介紹了解量子科技所需之背景知識、原理、相關研究與技術進展及其應用等，對於欲學習量子科學與技術有興趣的學生具有啟發及引導後續進階課程修習之助益。", "en": "This course is meant to introduce the background knowledge, principles, related research and technological advancements, as well as applications, necessary for understanding quantum technology. The course also provides inspiration and guidance for students interested in learning quantum science and technology, and assists them in subsequent advanced courses."}, "outline": {"ch": "本課程包含以下主題：1. 同調量子光學與量子干涉(兩週)2. 量子光源介紹(兩週)3. 量子記憶體簡介(兩週)4. 糾纏光子整形及調控(兩週)5. 應用於量子光學的半導體光偵測器介紹(一至兩週)6. 量子通訊協定簡介(一至兩週)7. 超導量子電路簡介(兩週)8. 量子演算法與量子網際網路(兩週)9. 拓樸能帶論與拓樸光子學簡介(兩週)", "en": "This course includes the following topics.1. Coherent transit and quantum interference (two weeks)2. Introduction to Quantum Light Sources (two weeks)3. Introduction to Quantum memory (two weeks)4. Shaping of entangled photons(two weeks)5. Introduction to semiconductor based photodetectors for quantum photonics (1 to 2 weeks)6. Introduction to quantum communication protocol (1 to 2 weeks)7. Introduction to superconducting quantum circuits (two weeks)8.Quantum algorithms and quantum Internet (two weeks)9. Introduction to topological band theory and topological photonics(two weeks)"}, "textbook": {"ch": "References:1. M. D. Eisaman, J. Fan, A. Migdall, S. V. Polyakov, “Invited review article: Single-photon sources and detectors,” Rev. Sci. Instrum. 82, 071101 (2011).2. Maria Tengner, Photonic Qubits for Quantum Communication, Doctoral Thesis, KTH School of Information and Communication Technology, Stockholm, Sweden (2008).3. P. Krantz et al., “A quantum engineer‘s guide to superconducting qubits,” Applied Physics Reviews 6, 021318 (2019).4. Pierre Meystre and Murray Sargent, “Elements of Quantum Optics”, third edition, Springer (2013), chapter 12, coherent transit.5. Alexander I. Lvovsky, Barry C. Sanders, and Wolfgang Tittel. “Optical quantum memory.“ Nature photonics 3, 706 (2009).6. Kok, Pieter, and Brendon W. Lovett. Introduction to optical quantum information processing. Cambridge university press, 2010.7. Modern Semiconductor Device Physics, Sze, John Wiley ＆ Sons, (1998)8. High-Speed Semiconductor Lasers and Photodetectors, CLEO/QELS’99 Conference Short Course Notes (Professor John Bowers)", "en": "References:1. M. D. Eisaman, J. Fan, A. Migdall, S. V. Polyakov, “Invited review article: Single-photon sources and detectors,” Rev. Sci. Instrum. 82, 071101 (2011).2. Maria Tengner, Photonic Qubits for Quantum Communication, Doctoral Thesis, KTH School of Information and Communication Technology, Stockholm, Sweden (2008).3. P. Krantz et al., “A quantum engineer‘s guide to superconducting qubits,” Applied Physics Reviews 6, 021318 (2019).4. Pierre Meystre and Murray Sargent, “Elements of Quantum Optics”, third edition, Springer (2013), chapter 12, coherent transit.5. Alexander I. Lvovsky, Barry C. Sanders, and Wolfgang Tittel. “Optical quantum memory.“ Nature photonics 3, 706 (2009).6. Kok, Pieter, and Brendon W. Lovett. Introduction to optical quantum information processing. Cambridge university press, 2010.7. Modern Semiconductor Device Physics, Sze, John Wiley ＆ Sons, (1998)8. High-Speed Semiconductor Lasers and Photodetectors, CLEO/QELS’99 Conference Short Course Notes (Professor John Bowers)"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "80", "en": "80"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "1. 書面報告 60％2. 期末考 40％", "en": "1. 書面報告 60％2. 期末考 40％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "預約制", "en": "by appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "物理及資訊", "en": "物理及資訊"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "自然環境的觀察及處理", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["作業練習", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "發掘問題與分析", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "資訊蒐集與整理", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考與批判", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "創造與多元思維", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "團隊合作與溝通", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "自信與專業表達", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Observation and processing of the environment", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Exploration and analysis", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Information collection and collation", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Independent thought and criticism", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Creativity and multiple thinking", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Teamw